Dildo.title: Dildo
Dildo.byline: Dildo is a town of 803 people (2021) by Trinity Bay, on the Avalon peninsula in Newfoundland in the province of Newfoundland and Labrador, Canada.

Dili.title: Dili
Dili.byline: Dili is a city of 222,000 people (2015) on the northern coast of East Timor, squeezed along the narrow plains between the central mountains which run the length of the Timor and the Ombai Strait.

Dilijan.title: Dilijan
Dilijan.byline: Dilijan is a town with mild climate and fresh air to the northeast of Yerevan.
